Base spacing unit (2px). All spacing scales are multiples of this value. Figma variable type: SPACING.
010 spacing (2px). Use for micro spacing needs.
020 spacing (4px). Use for tight spacing between small elements.
030 spacing (8px). Use for padding inside compact components.
040 spacing (16px). Use for default padding and margins.
050 spacing (24px). Use for section padding and larger margins.
060 spacing (32px). Use for major section spacing.
070 spacing (40px). Use for large vertical rhythm.
080 spacing (48px). Use for major vertical spacing.
090 spacing (64px). Use for hero section spacing.
100 spacing (80px). Use for large hero spacing.
110 spacing (96px). Use for extra large spacing.
